  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a global, multi-center, prospective, randomized, controlled study of the safety and
      effectiveness of renal denervation with the OneShot Renal Denervation System in patients with
      uncontrolled hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
